esigned%20a%20minimal%20wallet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20brings%20in%20more%20revenue%20in%20a%20month%20than%20he%20used%20to%20make%20in%20an%20entire%20year%20from%20his%20day%20job.%20They%20both%20started%20their%20e-commerce%20companies%20as%20side%20hustles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESure%2C%20it%20took%20time%20and%20commitment%20to%20create%20a%20product%20and%20build%20a%20brand%2C%20but%20their%20descriptions%20of%20launching%20Amazon%20shops%20did%20seem%20relatively%20straightforward.%20Fu%2C%20who%20has%20a%20background%20in%20consulting%2C%20relied%20on%20free%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20get%20started.%20Reeves%20signed%20up%20for%20Helium%2010%2C%20a%20popular%20software%20that%20Amazon%20sellers%20use%20to%20grow%20their%20online%20businesses.%20Included%20in%20the%20subscription%20is%20an%20online%20course%20about%20FBA%20(fulfillment%20by%20Amazon)%20that%20he%20tuned%20into.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20conversations%20got%20me%20thinking%3A%20Is%20starting%20a%20profitable%20Amazon%20business%20%E2%80%A6%20simple%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWere%20these%20e-commerce%20whizzes%20just%20that%3A%20whizzes%3F%20Or%2C%20could%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%2031-year-old%20reporter%20with%20some%20savings%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20free%20hours%20after%20work%20%E2%80%94%20make%20money%20selling%20things%20online%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20decided%20to%20find%20out%20for%20myself%20and%20document%20each%20detail%20of%20the%20process%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bd779de-b816-47ba-aabc-0edb9d611cd3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20a%20friend%20to%20double%20my%20%245%2C000%20budget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20considered%20how%20much%20of%20my%20own%20money%20I%20wanted%20to%20invest%20in%20this%20experiment%2C%20%245%2C000%20seemed%20reasonable.%20It%20was%20enough%20to%20launch%20something%20(after%20all%2C%20Fu%20started%20her%20Amazon%20store%20with%20just%20%242%2C000)%2C%20and%20it%20was%20an%20amount%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20losing%20if%20no%20one%20ended%20up%20buying%20my%20product.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20bigger%20budget%20would%20be%20better%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20always%20heard%20that%20startups%20cost%20twice%20as%20much%20and%20take%20twice%20as%20long%20as%20you%20think%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20an%20easy%20solution%3A%20Double%20the%20founders%20to%20double%20the%20budget.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20cofounder%2C%20a%20friend%20and%20former%20roommate%2C%20wasn't%20hard%20to%20find.%20He%20lived%2010%20paces%20down%20the%20hall%20from%20me%20at%20the%20time%20in%20our%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20LA.%20Both%20former%20collegiate%20tennis%20players%2C%20we'd%20met%20playing%20a%20different%20racket%20sport%20called%20paddle%20tennis%20at%20Venice%20Beach.%20Like%20me%2C%20he%20spent%20more%20time%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategies-money-saving-how-to-save-build-wealth-side-hustle-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eteaching%20tennis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20playing%20it%20since%20graduating.%20Our%20laundry%20room%2C%20which%20doubled%20as%20communal%20storage%20space%2C%20overflowed%20with%20rackets%2C%20ball%20hoppers%2C%20and%20tennis%20shoes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe'd%20been%20toying%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20an%20e-commerce%20business%20since%20the%20spring%20of%202023%20when%20I%20mentioned%20one%20of%20the%20Amazon%20stories%20I%20was%20working%20on.%20He%20was%20as%20curious%20as%20I%20was%20and%20also%20had%20the%20savings%20and%20bandwidth%20to%20dedicate%20to%20a%20side%20project.%20Double%20the%20founders%20would%20not%20only%20mean%20double%20the%20budget%20but%20double%20the%20skillset%20and%20double%20the%20network.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20third%20roommate%20was%20also%20entrepreneurial%2C%20juggling%20several%20side%20hustles%20outside%20his%20day%20job.%20That%20spring%2C%20our%20common%20room%20transformed%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20war%20room.%20Some%20of%20our%20early%20steps%20included%20messing%20around%20with%20Helium%2010%2C%20searching%20for%20high-demand%20products%2C%20and%20doing%20outreach%20on%20Alibaba%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20find%20and%20communicate%20with%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20project%20slowed%20down%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance-money-investing-goals-after-move-to-new-york-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20moved%20to%20NYC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20summer.%20We%20lost%20our%20war%20room%20and%2C%20with%20it%2C%20momentum%2C%20but%20recommitted%20in%20the%20winter%20of%202023.%20We%20made%20a%20financial%20commitment%20%E2%80%94%20we%20would%20each%20put%20up%20%245%2C000%20of%20our%20own%20savings%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20experts%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20advice.%20The%20more%20people%20we%20told%20about%20our%20project%2C%20the%20more%20obligated%20we%20felt%20to%20follow%20through.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20needed%20all%20the%20accountability%20we%20could%20get.%20Anyone%20can%20dream%20up%20an%20idea%20in%20their%20common%20room%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20fun%20and%20easy%20part%20%E2%80%94%20but%20taking%20that%20idea%20and%20turning%20it%20into%20something%20tangible%20requires%20commitment%2C%20momentum%2C%20and%20guidance.%20The%20execution%20part%20is%20the%20really%20hard%20part%2C%20especially%20when%20you're%20both%20working%20full-time%2C%20have%20steady%20paychecks%2C%20and%20don't%20necessarily%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eneed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20business%20to%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20half%20as%20hard%2C%20