20a%20severe%20hit%20since%20the%20military%20stand-off%20in%20Ladakh%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Beijing's%20%26quot%3Bunilateral%26quot%3B%20actions%20of%20violating%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20the%20de-facto%20boundary%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bilateral%20talks%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20Jinping%20took%20place%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20Summit%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Kazan%20in%20Russia.%20It%20happened%20less%20than%2072%20hours%20after%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20talks%20-%20both%20at%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20levels%20-%20ensuring%20that%20the%20status%20quo%20returns%20to%20what%20it%20was%20before%20May%202020%2C%20when%20the%20stand%20off%20in%20Ladakh%20began%20with%20the%20military%20clash%20in%20Galwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20patrolling%20arrangement%20comes%20four%20years%20after%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20clash%20and%20signals%20a%20move%20towards%20de-escalation%20in%20a%20region%20where%20both%20countries%20stationed%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20underscored%20the%20upturn%20in%20the%20India-China%20relation%20following%20a%20consensus%20on%20patrolling%20arrangement%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20that%20had%20faced%20multiple%20hiccups%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20couple%20of%20brief%20interactions%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20Jinping%20since%20the%202020%20Galwan%20clash%20-%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Indonesia's%20Bali%20in%20November%202022%20and%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20South%20Africa's%20Johannesburg%20in%20August%202023.%20However%2C%20these%20were%20not%20bilateral%20meetings%20where%20trade%2C%20economy%20and%20other%20factors%20were%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20no%20direct%20flight%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20for%20four%20years.%20Visa%20for%20Chinese%20technicians%20was%20granted%20after%20extra%20layers%20of%20security%20and%20investments%20from%20companies%20based%20in%20neighbouring%20countries%20needed%20extra%20vetting%20and%20security%20clearances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20of%20the%20bilateral%20meeting%20will%20make%20it%20clear%20if%20trade%2C%20economic%20and%20people-to-people%20ties%20will%20return%20to%20normalcy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729687440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ftpivcurk_modi-xi-bilateral-india-china-bilateral-ians_625x300_23_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-chinas-xi-jinping-bilateral-starts-in-russia-first-since-2020-6856030%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20Jinping%20met%20in%20Russia%20today%20for%20the%20first%20bilateral%20meeting%20since%202019.%20Ties%20between%20India%20and%20China%20had%20taken%20a%20severe%20hit%20since%20the%20military%20standoff%20in%20Ladakh%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Beijing's%20%26quot%3Bunilateral%26quot%3B%20actions%20of%20violating%20the%20LAC.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-chinas-xi-jinping-bilateral-starts-in-russia-first-since-2020-6856030%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TVS%20Motor%20Company%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20rises%2045%25%20to%20Rs%20560.49%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729687310000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ftvs-motor-company-q2-results-net-profit-rises-45-to-rs-560-49-cr-124102301179_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20had%20reported%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%20386.34%20crore%20in%20the%20July%20to%20September%20quarter%20of%20last%20financial%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt