Punia%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20her%20personal%20view.%20She%20was%20our%20friend%2C%20and%20she%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20so.%20I%20can't%20say%20anything%20about%20what%20she%20has%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20both%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20joined%20the%20Congress%20before%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections.%20Phogat%20was%20given%20a%20ticket%20from%20the%20Julana%20constituency%20while%20Punia%20was%20made%20head%20of%20the%20party's%20national%20farmers%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20won%20the%20Julana%20Assembly%20seat%20in%20Haryana%2C%20defeating%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20candidate%20Yogesh%20Kumar.%20The%20former%20wrestler%20secured%20a%20victory%20with%20a%20margin%20of%205%2C761%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729685760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ftdjrrgfg_va_625x300_23_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fsold-her-integrity-babita-phogat-blasts-sakshi-malik-over-wrestlers-protest-claim-6856072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20a%20dig%20at%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20and%20former%20wrestler%20Babita%20Phogat%20alleged%20that%20she%20had%20sold%20her%20integrity%20to%20sell%20her%20book.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fsold-her-integrity-babita-phogat-blasts-sakshi-malik-over-wrestlers-protest-claim-6856072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20Makes%20Trump%20What%20He%20Is%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Falgql11o_donald-trump_625x300_23_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20by%20the%20standards%20of%20someone%20best%20known%20for%20scandal%2C%20corruption%2C%20and%20criminality%2C%20a%20recent%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20listing%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20controversial%20deeds%20makes%20for%20sober%20reading.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20the%20only%20president%20in%20American%20history%20impeached%20twice%20for%20high%20crimes%20and%20misdemeanours%2C%20the%20only%20president%20ever%20indicted%20on%20criminal%20charges%2C%20and%20the%20only%20president%20convicted%20of%20a%20felony%20(34%20counts%2C%20in%20fact)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20narrative%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20ran%20for%20president%20in%202016%2C%20Trump%20had%20been%20involved%20in%204%2C095%20lawsuits%2C%20in%20which%20he%20or%20his%20companies%20were%20defendants%20in%201%2C026%20cases%20related%20to%20not%20paying%20taxes%2C%20not%20paying%20overtime%2C%20not%20compensating%20hired%20companies%2C%20and%20failing%20to%20abide%20by%20contracts.%20He%20was%20forced%20to%20shell%20out%20%2425%20million%20to%20students%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20scamming%20them%2C%20was%20found%20liable%20for%20widespread%20business%20fraud%2C%20and%20had%20his%20real%20estate%20firm%20convicted%20in%20criminal%20court%20of%20tax%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEstimated%20by%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20be%20worth%20%245.5%20billion%2C%20he%20has%20paid%20less%20income%20tax%20than%20at%20least%20half%20of%20American%20taxpayers%2C%20year%20after%20year.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20smart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20boasted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Seven%20Characteristics%20That%20Define%20Trump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETony%20Schwartz%2C%20who%20ghostwrote%20Trump's%20bestseller%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Art%20of%20the%20Deal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20wrote%20recently%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20seven%20characteristics%20associated%20with%20antisocial%20personality%20disorder%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Diagnostic%20and%20Statistical%20Manual%20of%20Mental%20Disorders%3A%20deceitfulness%2C%20impulsivity%2C%20failure%20to%20conform%20to%20social%20norms%20with%20respect%20to%20lawful%20behaviour%2C%20irritability%20and%20aggressiveness%2C%20reckless%20disregard%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20self%20or%20others%2C%20consistent%20irresponsibility%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20remorse.%20I've%20observed%20all%20seven%20in%20Trump%20over%20the%20years%20and%20watched%20them%20get%20progressively%20worse.%20It's%20the%20last%20one%20-%20lack%20of%20remorse%20-%20that%20gives%20him%20license%20to%20freely%20exercise%20the%20other%20six.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20you%20count%20them%2C%20Trump%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20sexual%20misconduct%20by%2019%2C%2026%2C%20or%2067%20women.%20He%20has%20boasted%20about%20grabbing%20women%20by%20their%20private%20parts%20and%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20cheated%20on%20all%20three%20of%20his%20wives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20its%20history%2C%20America%20may%20send%20a%20criminal%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office.%20The%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20who%20served%20under%20Trump%20has%20called%20him%20%26quot%3Ba%20fascist%20to%20the%20core%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20dangerous%20man%20for%20this%20country%26quot%3B.%20His%20longest-serving%20White%20House%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20has%20echoed%20these%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20elected%2C%20Trump%20has%20said%20he%20would%20turn%20the%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Benemy%20within%26quot%3B%E2%80%94which%20he%20defines%20as%20anyone%20who%20crosses%20him%20or%20has%20crossed%20him%20in%20the%20past.%20To%20tackle%20urban%20crime%2C%20he%20suggests%20%26quot%3Bone%20hour%20of%20widespread%2C%20extrajudicial%20violence%20by%20the%20police%26quot%3B.%20Oh%2C%20and%20by%20the%20way%2C%20he%20has%20demanded%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20former%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20Trump's%20Unusual%20Rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20such%20a%20deceitful%2C%20narcissistic%2C%20and%20malicious%20man%20seek%20election%20to%20the%20most%20powerful%20office%20in%20the%20world%20for%20the%20third%20time%20as%20the%20head%20of%20a%20party%20once%20led%20by%20Abraham%20Lincoln%3F%20How%20does%20he%20stand%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20becoming%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%202024%20campaign%20rallies%20resemble%20vaudeville%20acts%20where%20he%20alternately%20portrays%20himself%20as%20the%20saviour%20and%20protector%2C%20hurls%20lies%20and%20insults%2C%20compares%20migrants%20to%20Hannibal%20Lecter%2C%20promises%20political%20violence%20(mass%20migrant%20evictions%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbloody%20story%26quot%3B)%2C%20and%20makes%20anti-democratic%20statements%20(such%20as%20prosecuting%20opponents%20and%20praising%20foreign%20dictators).%20He%20stumbles%20through%20words%20like%20%26quot%3Bdeportated%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bbureucats%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMidworsten%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BInsaniticy.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20recent%20rally%2C%20when%20words%20ran%20out%2C%20he%20bobbed%20and%20danced%20to%20music%20for%2039%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20such%20a%20candidate%20improve%20his%20poll%20ratings%20from%20winning%2041%25%20of%20the%20electoral%20college%20vote%20in%20September%2C%20after%20a%20disastrous%20debate%20with%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20to%20over%2050%25%20now%3F%20Most%20of%20his%20gains%20have%20come%20from%20the%20key%20swing%20states%20of%20Michigan%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ripples%20From%20The%20Mayflower%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20begin%20to%20seek%20answers%20to%20that%20question%2C%20one%20might%20explore%20the%20deep%20vein%20of%20emotional%20nativism%20in%20American%20history%3B%20it's%20only%20half-jokingly%20said%20that%20those%20who%20arrived%20on%20the%20Mayflower%20in%201620%20regard%20all%20who%20came%20later%20as%20outsiders.%20A%20more%20definitive%20starting%20point%20would%20be%201993%2C%20the%20year%20the%20US%20signed%20NAFTA%20(North%20American%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement).%20NAFTA%20led%20to%20the%20shuttering%20of%20over%2097%2C000%20factories%20in%20the%20US%2C%20primarily%20in%20the%20Midwest%20and%20Pennsylvania%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20around%20five%20million%20jobs%20as%20manufacturing%20moved%20to%20Mexico.%20The%20ripples%20have%20not%20ceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChancy%20Adams%2C%2043%2C%20lost%20his%20job%20at%20an%20iconic%20lock-making%20company%20in%20Milwaukee%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20as%20recently%20as%20March%202024%2C%20when%20the%20unit%20shut%20down%20without%20notice.%20He%20began%20working%20there%20in%202010%20for%20%2410%20an%20hour%20and%20moved%20up%20to%20a%20supervisory%20role%20at%20%2430.%20He%20even%20bought%20a%20house%20for%20his%20family%20of%20five%2C%20including%20four%20children.%20Now%2C%20he%20works%20two%20jobs%20a%20day%20and%20still%20earns%20less%20money.%20He%20does%20not%20plan%20to%20vote%20on%20November%205%3B%20if%20he%20does%2C%20it%20will%20certainly%20not%20be%20for%20Kamala%20Harris%E2%80%94maybe%20Trump.%20Adams%20is%20Black.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20declared%20his%20bid%20for%20the%20presidency%20in%20August%202015%2C%20he%20was%20not%20a%20political%20novice%2C%20as%20widely%20thought.%20He%20had%20fully%20developed%20his%20playbook%2C%20drawing%20on%20his%20sharp%20political%20instincts.%20He%20would%20be%20a%20populist%2C%20a%20demagogue%2C%20a%20Macho%20Man.%20He%20would%20cater%20to%20the%20basest%20instincts%20of%20man%2C%20mining%20anger%20and%20sowing%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttack%2C%20Attack%2C%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20personality%20was%20shaped%20by%20his%20father%20and%20his%20mentor%2C%20lawyer%20Roy%20Cohn%2C%20around%20three%20pillars%3A%20Attack%2C%20attack%2C%20attack%E2%80%94never%20say%20sorry%2C%20never%20admit%20defeat%2C%20and%20follow%20your%20gut%20instincts.%20His%20public%20image%20was%20constructed%20as%20that%20of%20a%20highly%20successful%20businessman%20on%20the%20hugely%20popular%20reality%20show%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Apprentice%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20obscured%20his%20massive%20inheritance%20and%20his%20six%20bankruptcies.%20Trust%20in%20politicians%20has%20dipped%20to%20a%20new%20low%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20Trump%2C%20the%20master%20of%20branding%2C%20never%20pretended%20to%20be%20one%E2%80%94in%20fact%2C%20quite%20the%20opposite.%20His%20Make%20America%20Great%20Again%20(MAGA)%20voter%20base%20was%20ready%20to%20be%20shaped%20into%20a%20cult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20August%202015%2C%20he%20had%20already%20built%20an%20electoral%20base%20of%2015%25%20of%20what%20would%20eventually%20become%20his%20MAGA%20support%20by%20long%20cultivating%20three%20populist%20audiences%3A%20listeners%20of%20ultra-right-wing%20conspiracy%20theorist%20podcasts%2C%20followers%20of%20professional%20wrestling%20(WWF)%20who%20enjoy%20the%20spectacle%20despite%20knowing%20it's%20scripted%2C%20and%20readers%20of%20tabloids%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Enquirer%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Common%20to%20all%20three%20groups%20is%20an%20inability%20to%20distinguish%20fantasy%20from%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20and%20behavioural%20scientists%20have%20offered%20a%20range%20of%20insights%20into%20human%20behaviour%20that%20explain%20Trump's%20enduring%20appeal.%20Social%20status%20is%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20motivators%20for%20human%20behaviour%2C%20and%20citizens%20care%20much%20more%20about%20relative%20losses%20than%20about%20equivalent%20gains.%20Across%20developed%20democracies%2C%20the%20lower%20people%20feel%20their%20social%20status%20is%2C%20the%20more%20inclined%20they%20are%20to%20vote%20for%20anti-establishment%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Popularity%20And%20Fears%20Among%20Whites%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%20men%20react%20more%20aggressively%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20status%20than%20any%20other%20group%20in%20US%20society%2C%20and%20there%20were%20many%20warning%20signs%20flashing%20for%20them%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%20While%20non-college-educated%20white%20men%20bore%20the%20brunt%20of%20NAFTA%2C%20college-educated%20elites%20benefited%20from%20the%20growing%20digitalisation%20and%20financialisation%20of%20the%20economy.%20Much%20of%20Trump's%20appeal%20stems%20from%20his%20ability%20to%20turn%20the%20shame%20of%20downward%20mobility%20among%20white%2C%20non-college-educated%20individuals%20into%20a%20sense%20of%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20insult%20to%20injury%2C%20men%20were%20feeling%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20growing%20feminisation%20of%20US%20society%2C%20with%20girls%20outscoring%20boys%20in%20school%20and%20women%20outnumbering%20men%20in%20college%20admissions.%20The%20dominant%20dread%20among%20white%20men%20became%20the%20%26quot%3Bfear%20of%20falling%26quot%3B%E2%80%94anxiety%20that%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20economic%20or%20cultural%20shocks%2C%20they%20might%20descend%20further%20down%20the%20social%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20politics%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20dominated%20by%20high-status%20professionals%20in%20both%20parties.%20Their%20alienation%20from%20the%20underclass%2C%20along%20with%20the%20erosion%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20blue-collar%20base%2C%20was%20best%20reflected%20in%20Hillary%20Clinton's%20characterisation%20of%20Trump's%20supporters%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbasket%20of%20deplorable.%26quot%3B%20This%20constituency%20of%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20losers%20of%20modernisation%20found%20themselves%20without%20any%20mainstream%20political%20actors%20willing%20to%20represent%20and%20defend%20their%20way%20of%20life%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20one%20commentator%20noted.%20Enter%20Trump%20with%20the%20Authentic%20Appeal%20of%20the%20Lying%20Demagogue%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20greater%20his%20willingness%20to%20antagonise%20the%20establishment%20by%20making%20himself%20persona%20non%20grata%2C%20the%20more%20credible%20his%20claim%20to%20be%20his%20constituency's%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commentator%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Makes%20MAGA%20So%20Appealing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERacial%20animus%20and%20general%20resentment%20toward%20minorities%20among%20whites%E2%80%94particularly%20Blacks%2C%20Hispanics%2C%20Muslims%2C%20and%20LGBTQ%2B%20individuals%2C%20who%20are%20more%20inclined%20to%20vote%20Democrat%E2%80%94are%20among%20the%20strongest%20forces%20binding%20MAGA%20supporters.%20Trump%20built%20on%20this%20animus%20to%20incite%20fear%20of%20migrants.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20claims%20that%2020-25%20illegal%20migrants%20are%20%26quot%3Bterrorising%26quot%3B%20the%20US%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20according%20to%20the%20nonpartisan%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%2C%209%20million%20migrants%20have%20entered%20the%20country%20under%20Biden%2C%20of%20which%20half%20may%20be%20illegal.%20He%20began%20targeting%20migrants%20in%202016%2C%20labelling%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Brapists%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcriminals%26quot%3B.%20Today%2C%20he%20holds%20them%20responsible%20for%20high%20home%20prices%2C%20unemployment%2C%20infectious%20diseases%2C%20rising%20car%20insurance%20costs%2C%20unsafe%20elections%2C%20and%20even%20missing%20house%20pets.%20Not%20coincidentally%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Americans%20support%20mass%20deportation%20of%20illegal%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmerican%20Myths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20word%20on%20Trump's%20enduring%20appeal%20rests%20with%20historian%20Richard%20Slotkin.%20The%20professor%20of%20American%20Studies%20argues%20that%20Trump%20rides%20on%20several%20key%20American%20myths.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20'Myth%20of%20the%20Frontier'%2C%20which%20posits%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20white%20wealth%20was%20predicated%20on%20expansion%20to%20the%20beyond%20and%20the%20subjugation%20of%20Native%20Americans%2C%20thereby%20embedding%20racial%20exclusion%20as%20a%20societal%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Slotkin%2C%20Trump's%20MAGA%20appeal%20also%20rests%20on%20the%20'Myth%20of%20the%20Lost%20Cause'%E2%80%94the%20South's%20yearning%20for%20the%20days%20before%20the%20Civil%20War.%20This%20myth%2C%20Slotkin%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3Bcelebrates%20the%20Old%20South%20and%20its%20culture%2C%20and%20justifies%20violence%2C%20sometimes%20extreme%2C%20first%20to%20defend%20and%20then%20to%20restore%20its%20traditional%20structures%20of%20patriarchy%20and%20white%20supremacy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%202024%20campaign%20rhetoric%2C%20Slotkin%20notes%2C%20follows%20the%20'Lost%20Cause'%20playbook.%20%26quot%3BHe%20invokes%20fear%20of%20racial%20pollution%20by%20characterising%20liberal%20policies%20on%20immigration%20as%20the%20poisoning%20of%20the%20American%20bloodstream.%20He%20identifies%20himself%20as%20the%20agent%20of%20his%20people's%20retribution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20refuted%20all%20charges%20against%20him%E2%80%94personal%2C%20political%2C%20or%20relating%20to%20his%20business%20dealings%E2%80%94and%20has%20asserted%20that%20the%20true%20judgment%20of%20the%20American%20people%20will%20be%20delivered%20on%20November%205.%20That%20will%20be%20the%20day%20the%20American%20electorate%20demonstrates%20how%20good%2C%20or%20otherwise%2C%20they%20are%20at%20judging%20a%20person's%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ajay%20Kumar%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist.%20He%20is%20former%20Managing%20Editor%2C%20Business%20Standard%2C%20and%20former%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20The%20Economic%20Times.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729685700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fg52btqeo_donald-trump_625x300_23_O