C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20liked%20the%20discounts%20I%20got%20for%20bundling%20insurance%2C%20but%20it%20was%20worth%20it%20to%20switch.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20household%20saw%20not%20just%20one%20but%20two%20car%20accidents%20in%20the%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20both%20thanks%20to%20my%20less-than-experienced%20teenage%20boys.%20This%20isn't%20too%20shocking%2C%20as%20teens%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nih.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fnews-releases%2Fteen-crash-risk-highest-during-first-three-months-after-getting-drivers-license%5C%22%3Eeight%20times%20more%20likely%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20in%20a%20car%20crash%20or%20near%20miss%20during%20their%20first%20year%20of%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20no%20one%20was%20hurt%2C%20as%20the%20collisions%20were%20both%20fender%20benders.%20The%20damage%20to%20my%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20however%2C%20was%20much%20more%20extensive.%20We%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fprogressive-car-insurance-review%5C%22%3EProgressive%20car%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20company%20wanted%20to%20nearly%20double%20our%20insurance%20premiums%20after%20the%20accidents!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20paying%20far%20less%20than%20that%20by%20proactively%20taking%20steps%20to%20reduce%20what%20we%20paid%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fcheapest-car-insurance-teenagers%5C%22%3Ecar%20insurance%20with%20teenagers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20renewal%20offer%20was%20nearly%20%246%2C000%20a%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInsurance%20isn't%20cheap%20when%20you%20have%20multiple%20teen%20drivers%20and%20multiple%20cars.%20Before%20the%20accidents%2C%20we%20paid%20%241%2C548%20for%20a%20six-month%20insurance%20policy.%20This%20covered%20a%20minivan%2C%20a%20truck%2C%20and%20the%20beater%20that%20my%20son%20drove%20to%20school.%20The%20policy%20also%20covered%20my%20husband%2C%20my%2017-year-old%20licensed-driver%20son%2C%20my%2015-year-old%20permitted%20son%2C%20and%20me.%20Up%20to%20that%20point%2C%20everyone%20had%20decent%20driving%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20renewal%2C%20we%20upgraded%20two%20of%20our%20vehicles.%20Based%20on%20the%20new%20monthly%20charges%20for%20each%20upgrade%2C%20this%20would%20have%20increased%20the%20renewal%20by%20%241%2C320.%20We%20expected%20the%20new%20policy%20to%20be%20around%20%242%2C868%2C%20along%20with%20a%20modest%20increase.%20But%20thanks%20to%20the%20accidents%2C%20the%20renewal%20offer%20was%20a%20whopping%20%245%2C899%20for%20six%20months%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%20%2412%2C000%20a%20year%20just%20to%20drive%20our%20cars!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20being%20appalled%20at%20the%20hefty%20price%20increase%2C%20we%20simply%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20pay%20that%20much%20for%20insurance.%20We%20quickly%20began%20the%20search%20to%20reduce%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Faverage-car-insurance-cost%5C%22%3Ecar%20insurance%20premiums%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20we%20reduced%20our%20car%20insurance%20premiums%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20more%20affordable%20policy%20for%20%243%2C748%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20still%20painful%2C%20but%20not%20nearly%20as%20much%20as%20we'd%20originally%20thought.%20Here's%20what%20we%20did%20to%20get%20a%20better%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E1.%20Call%20an%20agent%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20step%20was%20to%20call%20our%20insurance%20agent.%20She%20understood%20our%20concerns%20and%20realized%20the%20need%20to%20reduce%20premiums.%20I%20explained%20the%20multiple%20factors%20at%20play%2C%20and%20she%20started%20hunting%20for%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20think%20applying%20online%20would%20help%20cut%20out%20agent%20commissions%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20cheaper%20policy.%20But%20firsthand%20experience%20has%20proven%20me%20wrong.%20My%20agent%20had%20access%20to%20details%20and%20options%20that%20I%20did%20not.%20She%20was%20acquainted%20with%20an%20insurer%2C%20Dairyland%2C%20that%20I%20had%20never%20heard%20of.%20The%20company%20specializes%20in%20drivers%20with%20tarnished%20driving%20records.%20Without%20her%20help%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20stuck%20paying%20far%20more%20than%20I%20should%20have%20simply%20because%20I%20lacked%20insider%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E2.%20Unbundle%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fbest-homeowners-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Ehomeowners%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20Progressive%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20nice%20multi-policy%20discount%20as%20a%20result.%20However%2C%20the%20discount%20didn't%20justify%20the%20doubled%20car%20insurance%20premiums.%20Because%20Dairyland%20doesn't%20write%20homeowner's%20policies%2C%20we%20had%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20that%20particular%20perk.%20Even%20with%20an%20independent%20homeowner's%20insurance%20policy%2C%20we%20still%20came%20out%20ahead%20by%20splitting%20up%20our%20insurance%20bundle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E3.%20Ditch%20brand%20loyalty%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20been%20with%20Progressive%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20long%20enough%20to%20get%20a%20loyalty%20discount.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20make%20the%20rate%20increase%20worth%20staying.%20I've%20hopped%20around%20insurance%20companies%20several%20times%20over%20the%20years.%20I%20realized%20that%20each%20insurer%20specializes%20in%20specific%20drivers%20and%20situations%2C%20so%20any%20time%20you%20add%20or%20remove%20a%20car%2C%20change%20drivers%2C%20or%20relocate%2C%20it's%20worth%20shopping%20around%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20getting%20a%20good%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E4.%20Pay%20in%20full%20upfront%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20Dairyland%20policy%20offered%20a%20handsome%20discount%20on%20our%20premiums%20(%24477)%20to%20pay%20the%20six-month%20policy%20upfront%20rather%20than%20in%20monthly%20installments.%20While%20it%20was%20a%20big%20purchase%2C%20we%20bit%20the%20bullet%20and%20got%20almost%20one%20month's%20worth%20of%20coverage%20free%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E5.%20Read%20the%20fine%20print%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20take%20the%20quote%20or%20bill%20as%20gospel.%20Check%20the%20fine%20print%20to%20ensure%20you%20got%20all%20the%20discounts%20you%20were%20promised.%20We%20got%20a%20surprised%20bill%20from%20Dairyland%20because%20the%20agent%20failed%20to%20submit%20the%20paperwork%20for%20a%20homeowner%20discount%2C%20and%20we%20got%20charged%20for%20the%20difference.%20I%20called%20my%20insurance%20agent%2C%20and%20she%20fixed%20the%20bill%20for%20me%2C%20saving%20me%20%24368.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-thousands-car-insurance-after-teens-car-accidents-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729683962000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712e393a0a0cc14f2226862%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-thousands-car-insurance-after-teens-car-accidents-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20kids%20both%20had%20fender%20benders%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20no%20one%20was%20hurt%2C%20but%20my%20wallet%20took%20a%20big%20hit.%20I%20saved%20on%20car%20insurance%20by%20giving%20up%20on%20brand%20loyalty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sisson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-thousands-car-insurance-after-teens-car-accidents-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindustan%20Unilever%20to%20separate%20ice%20cream%20business%20following%20board%20decision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729683918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt