%20he%20donated%20millions%20to%20a%20pro-Harris%20super-PAC%2C%20three%20sources%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20reportedly%20donated%20%2450%20million%20to%20Future%20Forward's%20nonprofit%20arm%2C%20which%20doesn't%20disclose%20donors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20billionaire%20didn't%20confirm%20or%20deny%20this%2C%20but%20told%20the%20Times%20this%20election%20was%20%26quot%3Bdifferent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Gates%20has%20privately%20said%20he%20donated%20about%20%2450%20million%20to%20a%20pro-Harris%20super-PAC%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F10%2F22%2Fus%2Felections%2Fbill-gates-future-forward-kamala-harris.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20multiple%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20Microsoft%20founder%2C%20who%20has%20not%20publicly%20endorsed%20either%20candidate%20for%20president%2C%20made%20the%20donation%20to%20Future%20Forward's%20nonprofit%20arm%2C%20Future%20Forward%20USA%20Action%2C%20three%20people%20briefed%20on%20the%20matter%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuture%20Forward%20USA%20Action%20does%20not%20disclose%20its%20donors%2C%20meaning%20any%20contributions%20would%20not%20be%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20sources%20said%20that%20Gates%20has%20talked%20about%20his%20donation%20with%20Mike%20Bloomberg%2C%20the%20former%20New%20York%20City%20mayor%2C%20among%20others%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20Times%2C%20Gates%20didn't%20confirm%20or%20deny%20the%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20election%20is%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20he%20supports%20candidates%20who%20show%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%26quot%3B%20commitment%20to%20improving%20healthcare%2C%20reducing%20poverty%2C%20and%20fighting%20climate%20change%20in%20the%20US%20and%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gates%20Foundation%20