levant%20information.%20It%20then%20autonomously%20goes%20through%20the%20steps%20in%20the%20form%20and%20submits%20the%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20example%20is%20representative%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20drudge%20work%20that%20people%20have%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Ringer%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20Anthropic%2C%20explains%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224a07339-b664-495a-b5e2-59dcddb49023%5C%22%3EI%3Cstrong%3Et's%20still%20'error-prone'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20readily%20admits%20that%20the%20model%20isn't%20perfect%20and%20makes%20some%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20stage%2C%20it%20is%20still%20experimental%20%E2%80%94%20at%20times%20cumbersome%20and%20error-prone%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20said%20in%20its%20blog%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20expects%20the%20tool%20to%20get%20better%20over%20time.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOne%20%26quot%3Bamusing%26quot%3B%20error%20that%20Anthropic%20mentioned%20in%20the%20blog%20includes%20when%20Claude%20briefly%20stopped%20a%20coding%20demo%20to%20search%20for%20photos%20of%20Yellowstone%20National%20Park.%20In%20another%20case%2C%20it%20accidentally%20clicked%20to%20stop%20recording%20a%20session%2C%20which%20meant%20it%20lost%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Anthropic's%20engineers%20made%20a%20request%20for%20the%20tool%20to%20order%20enough%20food%20to%20feed%20a%20group%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Claude%20selected%20pizza.%20Alex%20Albert%2C%20Anthropic's%20head%20of%20Claude%20relations%2C%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Falexalbert__%2Fstatus%2F1848777260503077146%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20used%20it%20to%20navigate%20the%20online%20food%20delivery%20platform%20DoorDash%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Babout%20a%20minute%20later%2C%20we%20saw%20Claude%20decided%20to%20order%20us%20some%20pizzas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5f62240-be08-4860-a873-008325ad7f3c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20early%20testers%20think%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEthan%20Mollick%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20Wharton%20School%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20is%20an%20early%20tester%20of%20the%20agent%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oneusefulthing.org%2Fp%2Fwhen-you-give-a-claude-a-mouse%3Futm_campaign%3Dpost%26utm_medium%3Dweb%26ref%3Dplatformer.news%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblogged%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20how%20he%20used%20it%20to%20help%20put%20together%20a%20lesson%20plan%20for%20high%20school%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20delegating%20a%20task%20rather%20than%20managing%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMollick%20also%20instructed%20it%20to%20create%20assignments%20based%20on%20Common%20Core%2C%20a%20set%20of%20educational%20standards%20for%20students%2C%20and%20to%20put%20them%20into%20a%20spreadsheet.%20He%20said%20that%20a%20chatbot%20would%20have%20needed%20his%20help%20to%20go%20through%20each%20step%2C%20whereas%20Claude%20downloaded%20a%20book%2C%20looked%20up%20lesson%20plans%20and%20Common%20Core%20standards%20online%2C%20and%20filled%20in%20the%20lesson%20plan%20spreadsheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20results%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20didn't%20spot%20any%20obvious%20errors.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20simply%20delegated%20a%20complex%20task%20and%20walked%20away%20from%20my%20computer%2C%20checking%20back%20later%20to%20see%20what%20it%20did%20(the%20system%20is%20quite%20slow).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraphic%20design%20platform%20Canva%20is%20testing%20out%20computer%20use%20to%20see%20how%20it%20can%20help%20with%20design%20creation.%20Danny%20Wu%2C%20the%20company's%20head%20of%20AI%20products%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fventurebeat.com%2Fai%2Fanthropic-new-ai-can-use-computers-like-a-human-redefining-automation-for-enterprises%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVentureBeat%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bdiscovering%20time-savings%20within%20our%20team%20that%20could%20be%20game-changing%20for%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1114737-90c7-4ad3-869c-5f5166b26b77%5C%22%3EUse%20with%20caution%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20advises%20people%20to%20take%20precautionary%20measures%20when%20using%20the%20tool%20to%20prevent%20unintended%20consequences%20like%20a%20cyberattack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20recommends%20safeguards%20to%20prevent%20prompt%20injection%2C%20a%20type%20of%20cyberattack%20in%20which%20a%20person%20prompts%20an%20AI%20model%20to%20change%20its%20intended%20behavior%20for%20nefarious%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Anthropic's%20model%20card%20addendum%20%E2%80%94%20a%20report%20card%20outlining%20some%20of%20the%20performance%20and%20safety%20considerations%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20suggests%20%26quot%3Busing%20a%20dedicated%20virtual%20machine%2C%20limiting%20access%20to%20sensitive%20data%2C%20restricting%20internet%20access%20to%20required%20domains%2C%20and%20keeping%20a%20human%20in%20the%20loop%20for%20sensitive%20tasks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275e639c0-8649-4bfa-91cb-63fae74490ac%5C%22%3EThe%20race%20to%20develop%20AI%20agents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20juggernauts%2C%20including%20rivals%20OpenAI%2C%20Cohere%2C%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20have%20jostled%20to%20develop%20new%20AI%20models%20with%20agentic%20capabilities%20%E2%80%94%20a%20system%20that%20responds%20with%20a%20degree%20of%20autonomy%20rather%20than%20responding%20to%20prompts.%20It's%20a%20subsector%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmulti-agent-systems-are-the-next-big-thing-in-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVCs%20are%20piling%20into%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20startups%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flondon-ai-startup-11x-raise-seed-funding-us-vc-benchmark-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E11x%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F928a22ba-1d04-4865-b854-5ebc5e53ea61%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolyAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20raising%20buzzy%20funding%20rounds%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20OpenAI's%20desktop%20app%20for%20ChatGPT%20allows%20users%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20chatbot%20and%20ask%20questions%20instantly%2C%20Claude's%20autonomous%20capabilities%20are%20a%20first%20in%20the%20ecosystem.%20Microsoft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ceo-marc-benioff-criticized-microsoft-copilot-ai-agents-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20announced%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20roll%20out%20the%20ability%20for%20companies%20to%20create%20their%20own%20autonomous%20AI%20agents%20next%20month%2C%20following%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ceo-marc-benioff-says-new-focus-on-ai-agents-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce's%20similar%20move%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20recently%20cinched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-funding-round-ai-tech-investors-venture-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%246.6%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20funding%20at%20a%20%24157%20billion%20valuation%2C%20which%20made%20it%20one%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20most%20valuable%20deals.%20Anthropic%20is%20far%20from%20reaching%20such%20dizzying%20funding%20heights.%20It's%20currently%20valued%20at%20around%20%2419.4%20billion%2C%20per%20PitchBook%20data%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20juggernaut%20is%20still%20attracting%20investor%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20biggest%20backer%20is%20Amazon%2C%20which%20has%20invested%20a%20total%20of%20%244%20billion%20in%20the%20company%20and%20partnered%20with%20it%20to%20make%20its%20AI%20models%20available%20on%20Amazon's%20generative%20AI%20platform%20Bedrock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20The%20Information%20