E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%2017%20when%20I%20campaigned%20for%20my%20father%20(former%20PM%20Rajiv%20Gandhi).%20Then%20I%20campaigned%20for%20my%20mother%20and%20brother%20and%20many%20of%20my%20colleagues.%20For%2035%20years%20I%20have%20been%20campaigning%20in%20different%20elections%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I%20am%20campaigning%20in%20an%20election%20and%20seeking%20your%20support%20for%20myself.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20different%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20and%20thanked%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20the%20election.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20my%20honour%20to%20represent%20you%20if%20you%20give%20me%20a%20chance.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%20she%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20visited%20Mundakkai%20and%20Churalmala%20in%20Wayanad%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20devastating%20landslides%20that%20claimed%20over%20400%20lives%20and%20displaced%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20the%20devastation%20with%20my%20own%20eyes.%20I%20saw%20children%20who%20lost%20their%20families.%20I%20met%20mothers%20who%20lost%20their%20children.%20I%20met%20people%20whose%20entire%20life%20was%20washed%20away.%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20one%20thing%2C%20each%20and%20every%20person%20I%20met%20was%20engaged%20in%20helping%20each%20other.%20They%20supported%20each%20other%20with%20courage%2C%20without%20greed%20and%20with%20compassion.%20To%20be%20part%20of%20your%20community%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20great%20privilege%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20what%20Wayanad%20had%20done%20for%20him%20cannot%20be%20expressed%20in%20words.%20%26quot%3BWayanad%20will%20have%20an%20official%20MP%20and%20an%20unofficial%20MP%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20they%20will%20both%20raise%20your%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressi