20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20year%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20won%20both%20Wayanad%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20seats%20and%20decided%20to%20retain%20the%20latter%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20bypoll.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20represented%20Wayanad%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%202019-2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20support%20for%20his%20sister%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20understand%20very%20well%20the%20relationship%20I%20share%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad.%20What%20Wayanad%20has%20done%20for%20me%20cannot%20be%20expressed%20in%20words.%20When%20feelings%20are%20really%20deep%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20express%20them%20is%20through%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20remind%20you%20Wayanad%20is%20the%20only%20constituency%20in%20the%20country%20that%20has%20two%20MPs%2C%20one%20is%20official%2C%20the%20other%20unofficial%2C%20and%20they%20will%20work%20together%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20speech%20replete%20with%20personal%20anecdotes%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20small%2C%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20my%20sister%20with%20her%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20used%20to%20tell%20her%2C%20Priyanka%2C%20you%20cannot%20go%20so%20far%20to%20look%20after%20your%20friends.%20She%20was%20willing%20to%20do%20anything.%20And%20sometimes%20the%20friends%20would%20not%20appreciate%20it.%20I%20would%20tell%20her%2C%20why%20do%20you%20do%20this%3F%20And%20she%20would%20say%20because%20I%20want%20to%2C%20and%20that%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20they%20don't%20appreciate.%20A%20person%20who%20is%20ready%20to%20do%20that%20for%20her%20friends%2C%20you%20can%20imagine%20what%20she%20is%20ready%20to%20do%20for%20family.%20When%20my%20father%20died%2C%20my%20sister%20looked%20after%20my%20mother.%20She%20was%2017%20years%20old.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20be%20wondering%20why%20I%20am%20telling%20you%20about%20her%20friends%20and%20family.%20The%20reason%20is%20Priyanka%20considers%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%20her%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20said%20he%20needed%20a%20favour%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20this%20rakhi%20on%20my%20hand%20that%20she%20made%2C%20I%20don't%20take%20it%20off%20till%20it%20breaks.%20This%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20a%20brother's%20protection%20for%20his%20sister.%20I%20request%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%2C%20look%20after%20my%20sister%2C%20protect%20my%20sister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20will%20put%20her%20entire%20energy%20into%20looking%20after%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad.%20And%20don't%20forget%20I%20am%20the%20unofficial%20MP%2C%20so%20I%20am%20allowed%20to%20come%20here%20and%20interfere%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%20she%20had%20been%20campaigning%20in%20elections%20for%2035%20years%20now%20but%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20she%20was%20seeking%20votes%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%2017%20when%20I%20campaigned%20for%20my%20father%20(former%20PM%20Rajiv%20Gandhi).%20Then%20I%20campaigned%20for%20my%20mother%20and%20brother%20and%20many%20of%20my%20colleagues.%20For%2035%20years%20I%20have%20been%20campaigning%20in%20different%20elections%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I%20am%20campaigning%20in%20an%20election%20and%20seeking%20your%20support%20for%20myself.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20different%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20and%20thanked%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20contest%20the%20election.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20my%20honour%20to%20represent%20you%20if%20you%20give%20me%20a%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729672620000%