is-biopic-he-is-a-great-actor%2Farticleshow%2F114499673.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fake%20Court%20Busted%20In%20Gujarat%2C%20Conman%20Who%20Posed%20As%20Judge%20Arrested%3A%20Police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20uncovered%20a%20nefarious%20scheme%20orchestrated%20by%20a%20man%20masquerading%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20his%20own%20fake%20tribunal%20and%20passing%20'judgements'%20since%202019%20especially%20in%20land%20deals%20in%20Gandhinagar%20area.%20Morris%20Samuel%20Christian%2C%20since%20arrested%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20deception%20that%20fooled%20many%20into%20believing%20they%20were%20in%20a%20legitimate%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20Christian%2C%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20this%20elaborate%20ruse%2C%20wielded%20his%20gavel%20to%20pass%20judgments%20in%20favour%20of%20his%20clients%2C%20all%20within%20the%20fabricated%20walls%20of%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bogus%20tribunal%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20real%20courtroom%2C%20worked%20undetected%20for%20years%2C%20with%20its%20roots%20tracing%20back%20to%20as%20early%20as%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitial%20probe%20suggested%20that%20Christian%20preyed%20on%20unsuspecting%20individuals%20entangled%20in%20land%20disputes%2C%20promising%20swift%20resolutions%20in%20exchange%20for%20hefty%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20assuming%20the%20role%20of%20a%20judge%2C%20he%20exploited%20the%20vulnerable%2C%20manipulating%20the%20course%20of%20justice%20for%20personal%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elaborate%20charade%20involved%20Christian's%20associates%20posing%20as%20court%20personnel%2C%20creating%20a%20facade%20of%20authenticity%20to%20dupe%20his%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elaborate%20theatrics%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20mock%20courtroom%20setting%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20lent%20an%20air%20of%20legitimacy%20to%20his%20deceitful%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Christ