0Khanna%E2%80%99s%20fondest%20memories%20are%20those%20with%20his%20family%20and%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20his%20hometown%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20distinctly%20remember%20how%20this%20%5B%3Cem%3Etikki%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F193273%2Flifestyle-health-street-food-recipes-millet-dosa-bhel-puri-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavourite%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20my%20cousins%20who%20would%20visit%20us%20from%20Kolkata%20and%20Mumbai.%20Nothing%20was%20done%20to%20make%20the%20potatoes%20crisp.%20Instead%2C%20they%20were%20fried%20to%20a%20great%20degree%20and%20then%20pressed%20on%20a%20hot%20%3Cem%3Etava%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pan)%20laden%20with%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20the%20late%2070s%2C%20each%20%3Cem%3Etikki%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20around%20Rs%2020%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20money!%20But%20the%20crispiness%20of%20those%20potatoes%20is%20very%20nostalgic%20for%20me.%20I%20still%20snack%20on%20them%20when%20I%20go%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Khanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99d%20be%20interested%20to%20know%20that%20this%20spot%20is%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20distinguished%20ones%20dotting%20the%20%E2%80%98food%20map%E2%80%99%20devised%20by%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20to%20celebrate%20his%20homecoming.%20The%20locales%20are%20set%20in%20stone%20and%20nothing%20is%20up%20for%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20global%20fame%20means%20the%20duo%20can%20no%20longer%20feast%20on%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246397%2Fstreet-food-vendors-pav-bhaji-american-civil-war-cotton-mill-portugese-mumbai-video-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estreet%20food)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20peace%20without%20500-odd%20people%20thronging%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20their%20favourite%20chef%20or%20(if%20they%E2%80%99re%20lucky)%20a%20selfie.%20And%20Khanna%20is%20ever-obliging%2C%20animatedly%20chatting%20up%20each%20vendor%20he%20visits.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20they%20were%20my%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20perfectly%20segues%20his%20next%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20take%20things%20for%20granted%20when%20we%20have%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20treasures%20his%20earliest%20memories%20of%20feasting%20on%20the%20food%20prepared%20by%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20experiences%20that%20he%20will%20remember%20forever%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371666%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20treasures%20his%20earliest%20memories%20of%20feasting%20on%20the%20food%20prepared%20by%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20experiences%20that%20he%20will%20remember%20forever%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-8-1729604730.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pictures%20from%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna's%20growing-up%20years%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-8-1729604730.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-8-1729604730-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-8-1729604730-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-8-1729604730-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-8-1729604730-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371694%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPictures%20from%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20growing-up%20years%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20tells%20me%20food%20is%20not%20the%20only%20thing%20on%20his%20mind.%20The%20women%20in%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20life%20%E2%80%94%20his%20mother%2C%20grandmother%2C%20and%20sister%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20making%20of%20the%20man%20and%20chef%20he%20is%3B%20their%20love%20forms%20the%20bedrock%20of%20his%20childhood%20and%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20in%20my%20team%20are%20first-generation%20Indian%20Americans.%20When%20describing%20visits%20they%20made%20back%20home%20during%20their%20summer%20vacations%2C%20they%20refer%20to%20their%20grandmothers%20as%20%E2%80%98healers%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20sheer%20magic%20their%20food%20evoked.%E2%80%9D%20Khanna%20attributes%20this%20to%20the%20simplicity%20of%20things.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20there%20was%20nothing%20attached%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358385%2Findian-grandmothers-running-food-ventures-businesses-pickles-chutneys-snacks-senior-citizen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrandmother%E2%80%99s%20food%20%3C%2Fa%3Eexcept%20for%20love%3B%20no%20expectation%2C%20no%20judgement.%20You%20were%20set%20free%20when%20having%20that%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-3-1729603781.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interiors%20of%20Bungalow%20have%20been%20done%20keeping%20Indian%20aesthetic%20in%20mind%3B%20the%20restaurant%20is%20an%20invitation%20to%20experience%20Indian%20culture%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-3-1729603781.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-3-1729603781-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-3-1729603781-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-3-1729603781-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-3-1729603781-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371670%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20interiors%20of%20Bungalow%20have%20been%20done%20keeping%20Indian%20aesthetic%20in%20mind%3B%20the%20restaurant%20is%20an%20invitation%20to%20experience%20Indian%20culture%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20today%2C%20the%20menu%20at%20Bungalow%20in%20East%20Village%2C%20New%20York%2C%20reflects%20these%20sensibilities.%20Time%20and%20again%2C%20the%20culinary%20virtuoso%20has%20reiterated%20how%20his%20latest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20last%20%E2%80%94%20gastronomic%20endeavour%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20street%20vendors%20of%20India%20and%20the%20crafts%20they%20have%20perfected%20over%20generations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hail%20from%20a%20small%20town%2C%20a%20small%20community%20where%20street%20food%20was%20the%20only%20way.%20In%20my%20growing%20up%20years%2C%20there%20was%20just%20one%20restaurant%20in%20Amritsar.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20food%20of%20street%20vendors%20that%20made%20us%20go%20%E2%80%98wow%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorrowing%20from%20the%20English%20word%20for%20%3Cem%3Ebangla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(single-story%20home)%2C%20coined%20during%20India%E2%80%99s%20colonial%20past%2C%20Bungalow%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307799%2Flondon-oldest-indian-restaurant-veeraswamy-history-nehru-gandhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvitation%20to%20experience%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20exceptional%20cuisine.%20With%20a%20menu%20featuring%20a%20repository%20of%20time-honoured%20recipes%20documented%20from%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%2028%20states%20in%20all%20its%20diversity%20and%20hues%2C%20the%20space%20invites%20you%20to%20reimagine%20classics%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBungalow%3A%20A%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99%20for%20Indian%20immigrants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecuring%20a%20reservation%20at%20this%20grand%20establishment%20is%20no%20easy%20feat%2C%20more%20so%20once%20the%20festive%20season%20in%20India%20sets%20in%20(October%20to%20December).%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20habit%20of%20going%20to%20lengths%20to%20recreate%20the%20Diwali%20magic%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20foodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProof%20of%20this%20lies%20in%20my%20conversation%20with%20h