ing%20to%20string%20together%20simple%20sentences%20in%20English.%20He%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20ever%20seen%20a%20computer%2C%20let%20alone%20known%20how%20to%20operate%20one.%20So%2C%20when%20brand%20new%2C%20shiny%20laptops%20found%20their%20way%20into%20his%20village%20of%20Jharagogua%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Deogarh%20district%2C%20Roshan%20was%20spellbound%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20peers%20were%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can%20distinctly%20hear%20them%20jostling%20each%20other%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20ensure%20each%20of%20their%20voices%20comes%20through%20the%20phone%20clearly.%20They%20echo%20a%20similar%20sentiment%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20love%20learning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F275433%2Fcoding-for-children-online-classes-benefits-parenting-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20things%20on%20the%20compute%3C%2Fa%3Er.%20We%20can%20study%20Maths%2C%20Science%2C%20and%20English%20and%20also%20play%20games.%20We%20learn%20everything%20at%20the%20centre%20only.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20silence%20after%20my%20follow-up%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20what%20do%20you%20learn%20at%20school%3F%E2%80%9D%20Roshan%20volunteers%20to%20answer%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20response%20finds%20backing%20in%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Oxford%20Human%20Rights%20Hub%20that%20directs%20attention%20to%20the%20Indian%20public%20education%20system%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cprioritises%20enrollment%20more%20than%20learning%E2%80%9D.%20Its%20%5Bthe%20system%E2%80%99s%5D%20perspective%20is%20missing%20the%20point%2C%20the%20report%20implies%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20schools%2C%20the%20teachers%20are%20completely%20ignorant%20of%20the%20subject%20and%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20students%2C%20and%20learning%20involves%20the%20children%20copying%20down%20lessons%20from%20blackboards%2C%20a%20completely%20mechanical%20exercise%20with%20l